PROBLEM 1 — PRINT 1 TO N
--------------------------------------------------------------
Print numbers from 1 to N using recursion.
Approach: print AFTER the recursive call (bottom-up).
    def print1ToN(n):
        if n == 0:       # base case: stop at 0
            return
        print1ToN(n - 1) # go down to 1 first
        print(n)         # then print on the way back up
